featured_reviews.review_id:
I pay high respect to the shrine. We are blessed to have such personalities who have served our deen.!! I have visited many times to this shrine. The head namely Altaf Ah from Kashmir is behaving rudely to people. He is creating this holy palace a hub of nepotism, corruption, and favoritism. We requested him a day before shelter but he refuted it as he is the owner of the property.
We are thankful to Fategarh shb shrine & our sikh brothers who gave us shelter later on. I'm requesting the managing body kindly intervene in it and stop such people from doing politics there. Kindly quickly drop him as head and appoint any other natural person who knows how to treat people, and respect all people irrespective ofreof region. Regards from the citizen of proud country of India
